---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Home">
  <section class="hero">
    <h1>Surfing Game</h1>
    <p class="tagline">A browser-based wave simulation exploring realistic ocean physics</p>
    <div class="cta-buttons">
      <a href="/game" class="btn btn-primary">Play Now</a>
      <a href="/blog" class="btn btn-secondary">Read the Blog</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="about">
    <h2>About the Project</h2>
    <p>
      This is an open-source experiment in simulating realistic wave behavior in the browser.
      We model wave energy propagation, shoaling (waves steepening as they approach shore),
      breaking waves, and foam dynamics—all rendered at 60fps on an HTML5 Canvas.
    </p>
    <p>
      The project serves as both a playable game and a learning resource for understanding
      wave physics, canvas rendering techniques, and visual regression testing strategies.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="features">
    <h2>Technical Highlights</h2>
    <div class="feature-grid">
      <div class="feature">
        <h3>Wave Energy Model</h3>
        <p>Energy fields propagate from the horizon, transforming through shoaling and breaking phases based on bathymetry (ocean floor depth).</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature">
        <h3>ASCII Matrix Testing</h3>
        <p>Inspired by RxJS marble diagrams, we test physics simulations using human-readable ASCII snapshots that show how matrices evolve over time.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature">
        <h3>Visual Regression</h3>
        <p>Automated screenshot comparisons catch rendering bugs before they ship, with Docker-based CI ensuring consistent baselines across environments.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature">
        <h3>Turborepo Monorepo</h3>
        <p>Organized as a monorepo with separate packages for core physics, visual testing viewer, and this website—all sharing types and utilities.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .hero {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 4rem 1rem;
  }

  .hero h1 {
    font-size: 3rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .tagline {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .cta-buttons {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .btn {
    padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 0.5rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: background-color 0.2s;
  }

  .btn-primary {
    background: var(--color-primary);
    color: white;
  }

  .btn-primary:hover {
    background: var(--color-primary-dark);
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .btn-secondary {
    background: var(--color-bg-secondary);
    color: var(--color-text);
    border: 1px solid #ddd;
  }

  .btn-secondary:hover {
    background: #eee;
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .about {
    max-width: 720px;
    margin: 0 auto 3rem;
    padding: 0 1rem;
  }

  .about h2 {
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .features {
    padding: 2rem 0;
  }

  .features h2 {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .feature-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  .feature {
    padding: 1.5rem;
    background: var(--color-bg-secondary);
    border-radius: 0.5rem;
  }

  .feature h3 {
    color: var(--color-primary);
  }
</style>
